│   │   │     - **Guest User:** Navigates to `/optional-signup`.
│   │   │   - Uses `useAuth` to determine if a user is authenticated.
│   │   │   - Uses `@/components/Navbar` and `@/components/Footer`.
│   │   │   Usage: Step in the multi-step onboarding flow. 
